覽等活動。Desire 22 Pro 還支援在 VIVERSE 進行包括購買 NFT 的數碼資產交易。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/06/29/uber-lfyt-gig-workers-teslas-evs-gas-prices-profit/life-tech/auto/attachment/0629-4a-9/" rel="attachment wp-att-1107446"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/0629-4a-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/0629-4a-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/0629-4a-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/0629-4a.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>HTC Desire 22 Pro 將會在 7 月 1 日於臺灣上市，定價為 11,990 臺幣（約 3,143 港元），有波光金和星夜黑兩種機身顏色選擇。現時購買可獲元宇宙上市早鳥禮包，包括 HTC 無線充電板、雙料防震殼、獨家限定貓。美術館 NFT 盲盒的兩款 NFT 非同質化代幣。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/7098/6421434">UDN</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
